                <td><span class="talkHeader">Forget Passwords, Use Persona</span>
                    <p class="talkDescription">Ember Fest uses Mozilla Persona for registration and sign-in. Come learn what Persona is, how Persona works, and how you can use Persona to get rid of passwords in your own applications. This will be a short introductory talk followed by an audience-driven deep dive into Persona's philosophy, design, and implementation.</p>
